    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Savanna Sam</strong> is a <strong>3D action game</strong> where you take over the controls of Sam’s trusty biplane and help him on his dangerous journey. Make sure Sam reaches his destination and can make his delivery!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gameplay of Savanna Sam is similar to console classic <strong>Star Fox</strong>, replacing the shooting with even more barrel rolls!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Evade all obstacles</strong> in the colorful levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make sure both Sam and his plane reach the end of the level without a scratch!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect</strong> all the <strong>golden rings and items</strong> popping up throughout the levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rotate</strong> Sam to fit through any gap.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Sam’s neck to collect even hard to reach items.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through the <strong>story mode</strong> to see how Sam’s adventure unfolds.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to make the trip through the Savanna?</p>",
